  "texts": [
    "For instance, flavor profiles commonly consumed in non-Western regions may be underrepresented, leading to models that fail to accommodate global variation in taste and smell preferences.",
    "Bias is also introduced by oversimplified assumptions embedded within model architectures, which may neglect complex interactions among sensory cues.",
    "Closely related to this issue is the quality and diversity of datasets used in sensory AI.",
    "Many datasets in this field are limited by small sample sizes, class imbalance, and inadequate demographic representation.",
    "These constraints hinder the scalability and robustness of AI systems (Apu et al. 2025)."
  ],
